  "name": "RPlog_The_Fall_of_Coreshan",
  "title": "The Fall of Coreshan",
  "summary": "The bounty hunter Morganna and her armored associate Tabl plot to capture the man Coreshan aboard the KOS station, with Morganna luring him alone into the KOS Gardens. She corners Coreshan, an artist nursing a drink over his sketchbook, and presses a blaster into his back, ordering him to come quietly. Coreshan reveals a desperate gambit: he has logged Morganna's secret into a file given to a contact who will expose her to the Empire, and claims a Jedi will receive his message if he dies, even confessing his love for her. When Morganna hesitates over a sketch of a scarred woman in her book, Coreshan suddenly attacks, shattering her knee and drawing his pistol. A frantic firefight erupts; Morganna, torn between rage and an unfamiliar flicker of honor, and Tabl, who needs Coreshan alive, finally bring him down with stun and kill fire. Coreshan survives, is cuffed, and Morganna, recovering her sketchbook, limps away from a victory that feels hollow to her.",
